Last Broadcast Date: Tue 17 May 2011
Matthew Bannister meets Kate and Gerry McCann, whose daughter Madeleine has been missing for four years. The couple describe the moment they realised Madeleine had disappeared from their holiday apartment in Portugal, the shock of becoming suspects themselves and their continuing search for their daughter. Show less